text: Lee Dong-hae () (born 15 October 1986 ), commonly known as just Donghae (), is a South Korean singer, songwriter and actor. He is best known as a member of the K-pop boy band Super Junior and its subgroup, Super Junior-M and Super Junior-Donghae & Eunhyuk. He is also one of the first four Korean artists to appear on Chinese postage stamps. ==References== Category:1986 births Category:J-pop singers Category:K-pop singers Category:Living people Category:SM Entertainment artists Category:South Korean actors Category:South Korean singers
